===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A small, short-tailed European [[rodent]], ''[[Cricetus]] [[frumentarius]]'', often kept as a [[pet]]. It is remarkable for having a [[pouch]] on each side of the jaw, under the skin, and for its migrations.
#: ''It is the cutest sight to see a '''hamster''' stuff his puffy cheeks with food; where is he going to store it?''
# {{context|zoology}} Any of various Old-world rodent species belonging to the subfamily ''Cricetinae''.

